        'title' => 'Trick Deck Structure',
        'desc' => 'Each module is framed differently so players can scan the homepage like a route board instead of a generic landing stack.',
    ],
    [
        'icon' => '03',
        'title' => 'Responsive Lift',
        'desc' => 'The same hierarchy holds on mobile, with cards reflowing into larger touch targets instead of shrinking into noise.',
